00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:39.440
Since then, I haven't made a New Year's resolution at all.

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:43.599
What is your New Year's resolution?

00:01:43.599 --> 00:01:48.720
If you can't make a New Year's resolution, what do you want to do this year?

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:51.519
I can't make a New Year's resolution,

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:59.919
