00:01:59.919 --> 00:02:03.120
So, in today's episode,

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:12.639
First, I would like to share the questions I looked back on last year and the questions I will ask myself this year.

00:02:12.639 --> 00:02:21.199
You often say that good quality questions make a good quality life, right?

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:24.880
So, I came up with five questions today.

00:02:24.880 --> 00:02:29.039
Okay, so the first one.

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:37.839
What do you think you are proud of looking back on last year?

00:02:37.839 --> 00:02:41.119
Before we talk about this year,

00:02:41.119 --> 00:02:46.160
