00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:49.919
It doesn't matter if it's small, so let's think about it.

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:58.559
Well, when we look back on a year, we usually reflect on it, right?

00:02:58.559 --> 00:03:04.320
I think we think, oh, this wasn't good, or I should have done this a little more,

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:10.960
