00:03:23.199 --> 00:03:31.440
Well, I think there are quite a few people who go on to the next project without celebrating what they have achieved, right?

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:34.240
I was like that too.

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:39.440
It's important to reflect on and analyze what you have failed,

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:45.440
but I think it's just as important to celebrate what you have achieved.

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:53.199
So, I think it's better to think about what you have worked hard for a year and give yourself a reward.

00:03:53.199 --> 00:04:01.039
For example, when you work hard, you can go to a convenience store and buy a cheesecake that is more expensive than usual.

00:04:01.039 --> 00:04:05.919
I think it's better to give yourself a reward.

00:04:06.880 --> 00:04:17.279
I don't think it's easy to praise yourself for what you've done in this busy modern society,

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:22.399
