00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:29.040
Before you think about this year, first look back at last year.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:32.399
Do you look back at the end of the year?

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:39.279
I look back at what I've learned this year, what I've worked hard for this year,

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:44.880
