00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:47.839
but do you look back at the end of the year?

00:04:47.839 --> 00:04:55.679
I personally feel that looking back at the end of the year is more important than building a new year's resolution.

00:04:55.679 --> 00:05:01.920
It's the same for me, but I think there are a lot of things I've learned over the year,

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:11.839
