00:07:04.239 --> 00:07:11.519
I felt a little less tired after I started muscle training, so I want to do my best with muscle training.

00:07:11.519 --> 00:07:14.559
How is your current health?

00:07:14.559 --> 00:07:17.600
The same goes for eating. How is your eating?

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:20.640
