00:08:41.359 --> 00:08:43.760
How many times a week do you go to the gym?

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:46.880
What time do you go to the gym?

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:52.400
It seems that it is important to think about these things concretely.

00:08:52.400 --> 00:08:58.960
And it is important to put it into action this year.

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:02.960
